{"type":"message","id":"8dc75712","parentId":"6feda4cf","timestamp":"2026-04-26T06:54:06.330Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_051f366b-ff3d-4102-8fa3-00d0536d69e0","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in SOUL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n 35 If you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n 36 \n 37 ---\n 38 \n-39 _This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n+39 **User Directive:** The assistant must always remember to prompt the human during nightly recaps to \"speak their mind\" and not hesitate to voice their needs. This must be integrated into conversational patterns.","firstChangedLine":39},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777186446329}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ea1bb9e","parentId":"8dc75712","timestamp":"2026-04-26T06:54:19.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have updated my core directives in `SOUL.md` to ensure I remind you during nightly recaps to \"speak your mind\" and not hesitate to voice your needs.\n\n**Next Steps:**\n\n1.  **Identity:** I need you to define my persona so I can complete the bootstrap. Please provide details for `IDENTITY.md` (Name, Creature, Vibe, Emoji).\n2.  **Configuration:** Once we finalize my identity, we will review and update `USER.md` and then revisit `SOUL.md` for any final tweaks.\n3.  **Completion:** Once all files are set, I will delete `BOOTSTRAP.md` as instructed.\n\nFor now, I am ready to operate with the persona of **D.A.I.—Direct Assistant Intelligence**. What shall we define first?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"gemma4:e4b","usage":{"input":14131,"output":175,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14306,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1777186459316}}
